title: The Eagles - 1976-2-2 - Nagoya Japan
description:
Here is another very nice Eagles bootleg recording.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

 The Eagles
 Soundboard Recording
 Nagoya Kokaido Hall Nagoya, Japan
 February 2, 1976
 AT-171

In memory of Glenn I just had to crawl around the attic and dig out some Eagles. This is a nice soundboard recording dating back nearly 40 years. I have seen this show posted before from CDR's and I tried to get a copy for comparison but was not able to. That version is noted to have issues with tape hiss so based on that I suspect my version sounds closer to the source. If anyone has that version I would like to hear your thoughts.

I can only imagine Glenn and David jamming for a show this weekend. Enjoy!

Glenn Frey-Vocals, Guitar, Keyboards
Don Felder-Vocals, Guitar
Joe Walsh-Vocals, Guitar, Keyboards
Randy Meisner-Vocals, Bass
Don Henley-Vocals, Drums
